-I was just trying to call you.

207
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:56,160
I was passing by.
Thought I'd give you a ride.

208
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,080
Thanks.

209
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,600
-Dhananjay.
-Jeh.

210
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:03,960
-Pleasure.
-Same.

211
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:07,680
Jeh owns this bar at Kala Ghoda.

212
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,040
Truck Bar.

213
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:13,120
-I'd love to check it out sometime.
-Love to have you.

214
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:19,400
Actually, he just got served a notice
by municipal authorities

215
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:21,480
regarding some violations, you know?

216
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:23,640
And Jeh never violated any laws.

217
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:26,840
So, it just feels like
they are after him. You know?

218
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:30,960
I think I can help you out.
The mayor is a close family friend.

219
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:32,720
Thank you.

220
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:38,160
It's nice of you to offer,
but I'm taking care of it. Thanks.

221
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:40,720
Sure.

222
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:43,760
Let me know if you change your mind.

223
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:53,560
Mr. Khan, with this company, the right
thing would be to establish a precedent.

224
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:58,240
I was thinking,
let's go completely offensive on this one?

225
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,160
Honestly...

226
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:03,280
