00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:07,200
Your mom is a great student.

519
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:10,280
Makes some brilliant analogies.

520
00:33:10,360 --> 00:33:11,360
I'm sure.

521
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:15,720
I'll see you on Saturday.

522
00:33:15,800 --> 00:33:17,120
Next class.

523
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:19,840
-See you. Bye.
-Bye.

524
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,480
Move.

525
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:30,080
It was a really excellent class.

526
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,680
Yeah, I can see that.

527
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:33,920
As in?

528
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:39,160
As in, paying special attention
to his special student.

529
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:44,520
-Siddhi, really?
-Seriously, Mommy?

530
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:47,320
You still doubt it
after Manohar's episode?

531
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:52,200
Let's go home, Raju.

532
00:34:06,840 --> 00:34:07,840
Caramel!

533
00:34:08,720 --> 00:34:10,840
-Wow!
-Hey, Caramel.

534
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:13,000
Hi, Caramel?

535
00:34:13,080 --> 00:34:15,000
Is your name Caramel? Hi, Caramel.

536
00:34:15,080 --> 00:34:17,120
Caramel, sit.

537
00:34:19,160 --> 00:34:22,600
Actually, we're closed right now.
Can you come back tomorrow?

538
00:34:22,640 --> 00:34:25,520
-No. We are just out on a walk.
-Hi.

539
00:34:26,200 --> 00:34:28,360
I run this bakery down the road.

540
00:34:28,440 --> 00:34:32,160
Caramel, she just barged in.
So, thought we would peep in.

541
00:34:34,160 --> 00:34:35,960
Please, peep all you like then.

542
00:34:36,040 --> 00:34:38,600
-You can come in.
-Thank you.

543
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:42,760
Come. Come on, Caramel.
Caramel, go inside.

544
00:34:44,040 --> 00:34:45,640
-Thank you.
-No problem.

545
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:03,040
What great energy.

546
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:09,320
-I'm Meher, by the way.
-Umang.

547
00:35:12,920 --> 00:35:14,640
Umang's Umami.

548
00:35:16,160 --> 00:35:17,480
The fifth taste.

549
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:21,560
That words can't describe.

550
